Create Columns, Measures 15   2) Create New Columns

      How to create new column (Duration column)

     - (1) Right click to the table that you want to create the new column

     - (2) Select New column

     - (3) Type Column name ---> "=" sigh ---> DAX

     - (4) Click Enter

          


   Column we need to create

  •       Create DURATION column in Fact_JobReferral table

      DAX

      DURATION = DATEDIFF(Fact_JobReferral[JobRefStartDate],Fact_JobReferral[JobRefEndDate],DAY)

  •      Create Refresh column in  Fact_JobReferral table

      DAX

      REFRESH = "Last Refresh as of " & MAX(Fact_JobReferral[JobReFactiveStatusUpdated])

  •    Create FORMAT DATE column in Fact_Submissions_Interview_Offer table

      DAX

     FORMAT DATE = FORMAT(Fact_Submissions_Interview_Offer[SubmissionDate],"mmm"" ""yyyy"

   3) Create new Mesures

     How to create new measure

    - (1) Right click on MEASURE table

    - (2) Select New Measure

    - (3) Type Measure Name ---> = sign ---> DAX

    - (4) Click Enter

    - (5) Repeat step (1) to (4) to create all Measures    

           

   


  

To create  Columns, Measures click the link below
